Package: spquery
Title: Queries on Spatial Raster Data
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Jakub", family = "Nowosad", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "nowosad.jakub@gmail.com", 
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1057-3721")))
Description: Performs several queries based on spatial raster data.
    It allows searching for areas with similar values to a query and 
    comparing values between two rasters based on a given distance measure.
